OL,7,FThe prime minister has warned that
OL,8,Fsocial media is not a "law-free zone",
OL,9,Fas ITV News Correspondent Ben Chapman
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FA man who encouraged people on
OL,13,FFacebook to attack a Leeds hotel
OL,14,Fhousing asylum seekers has been jailed
OL,15,Fin what is thought to be the first
OL,16,Fcase of its kind relating to the riots.
