OL,4,Cusers to attack hotel housing asylum
OL,5,Cseekers
OL,7,FJordan Parlour, 28, was sentenced to
OL,8,F20 months at Leeds Crown Court, over a
OL,9,Fpost about the Britannia Hotel, in the
OL,10,FSeacroft area of the city, which was
OL,11,Fhome to 210 refugees and asylum
OL,12,Fseekers.
OL,14,FThe court heard he wrote on Facebook:
OL,15,F"Every man and their dog should be
OL,16,Fsmashing f*** out Britannia Hotel."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
