OL,5,Cseekers
OL,7,FThe court heard Parlour posted the
OL,8,Fcomments after the hotel had been
OL,9,Ftargeted by people throwing missiles
OL,10,Fand breaking windows, and more attacks
OL,11,Fhappened later.
OL,13,FBodycam footage shows the moment
OL,14,FParlour was arrested
OL,16,FIt was also heard that his mother
OL,17,Fwrote a letter to court which said:
OL,18,F"We can only speculate he's been
OL,19,Fcaught up and swept away by emotions
OL,20,Fcirculating throughout the country."
