OL,7,FHe appeared to blow a raspberry as he
OL,8,Fwas led from the court.
OL,10,FRosemary Ainslie, acting head of the
OL,11,FCPS special crime and counter
OL,12,Fterrorism division, said: "Let me be
OL,13,Fabsolutely clear, people who think
OL,14,Fthey can hide behind their keyboards
OL,15,Fand stir up racial hatred should think
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,F"Jordan Parlour advocated violence
OL,19,Fthrough his online posts and risked
OL,20,Fthe safety of those staying and
OL,21,Fworking at the hotel.
