OL,7,FOn Wednesday images of 21 people were
OL,8,Fissued by South Yorkshire Police in
OL,9,Fconnection with violent disorder
OL,10,Foutside a hotel housing asylum seekers
OL,11,Fin Rotherham, and Humberside Police
OL,12,Freleased 16 images following unrest in
